
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "style" %>
    <%= javascript_tag "materialize" %>
    <%= javascript_tag "init" %>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
</head>
<body>
  <nav role="navigation">
    <div class="nav-wrapper container red lighten-2">
    <%= link_to "PARADiSE - By Local From Local", {:controller => 'homepage', :action => "index" }, {:class => "brand-logo white-text", :id => "logo-container" } %>
      <ul class="right hide-on-med-and-down">
        <li>
          <%= link_to "Home", {:controller => 'homepage', :action => "index" }, { :class => "white-text" } %>
        </li>
        <li>
          <%= link_to "Features", {:controller => 'features', :action => "index" }, { :class => "white-text" } %>
        </li>
        <li>
          <%= link_to "LOKADiSE", {:controller => 'lokadise', :action => "index" }, { :class => "white-text" } %>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <ul id="nav-mobile" class="sidenav">
        <li>
          <%= link_to "Home", {:controller => 'homepage', :action => "index" } %>
        </li>
        <li>
          <%= link_to "Features", {:controller => 'features', :action => "index" } %>
        </li>
        <li>
          <%= link_to "LOKADiSE", {:controller => 'lokadise', :action => "index" } %>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#" data-target="nav-mobile" class="sidenav-trigger"><i class="material-icons">menu</i></a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div id="index-banner" class="parallax-container" style=" min-height: 450px;">
    <div class="section no-pad-bot">
      <div class="container">
      <h1 style="opacity:0">weird</h1>
        <h1 class="center red-text text-lighten-2">Prototype Features</h1>

        <br><br>

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="parallax">
        <%= image_tag("background17.jpg")  %>
    </div>
  </div>


    <div class="section">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m5 center">
            <br><br>
          <%= link_to image_tag("sign_up.png", :size => "250x480"), 'https://marvelapp.com/113c7c94/screen/67632684', :target => 'blank' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <br><br>
            <h4 class="center" style="font-weight: bold">REGISTRATION</h4>
            <br>
            <h6 class="center" style="font-weight: bold">SIGN UP (Travelers)</h6>
            <p class="center" style="font-size:2vmin">Click the picture on the side for more, it is recommended to use PC</p>
            <ol>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you are the first user, click "SIGN UP" on the blue button on the bottom right
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                There are two options "TRAVELER" and "LOKADiSE", if you are a traveler, click "TRAVELER"
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                You are asked to fill in your data such as name, email and password. Click the data column to bring up the keyboard.            
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                When the keyboard appears, click on the keyboard and an illustration of your data will appear.            
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                After that, click "SIGN UP".
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                You have registered and entered Home.
            </li>
          </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m5 center">
            <br><br>
          <%= link_to image_tag("log_in.png", :size => "250x480"), 'https://marvelapp.com/113c7c94/screen/67632684', :target => 'blank' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <br><br>
            <h4 class="center" style="font-weight: bold">REGISTRATION</h4>
            <br>
            <h6 class="center" style="font-weight: bold">LOG IN</h6>
            <p class="center" style="font-size:2vmin">Click the picture on the side for more, it is recommended to use PC</p>
            <ol>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you already have an account, click "LOG IN" on the orange button at the bottom left.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                You are asked to fill in your e-mail and password data. Click the data column to bring up the keyboard.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                When the keyboard appears, click on the keyboard and an illustration of your data will appear.            
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                After that, click "SIGN UP".
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If successful, you enter the Home.
            </li>
          </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m5 center">
            <br><br>
          <%= link_to image_tag("home.png", :size => "250x480"), 'https://marvelapp.com/113c7c94/screen/67632684', :target => 'blank' %>
        </div>
        <div class="col s12 m6">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <br><br>
            <h4 class="center" style="font-weight: bold">HOME</h4>
            <p class="center" style="font-size:2vmin">Click the picture on the side for more, it is recommended to use PC</p>
            <ol>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you have entered "Home", you will see a prototype display features.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                You can scroll, then swipe left and right on the travel menu options (in the Tanjung Kelayang column) or click the next and previous symbols to see other travel options.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you are interested in traveling, click on the existing tourist destination you want to go, here, I design at Tanjung Kelayang. Click "Tanjung Kelayang" for more.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                You will be shown in detail the Tanjung Kelayang tourist destination. There are details about location, itinerary, include & exclude, Terms & Conditions, Do's & Dont's, and personal equipment list.
            </li>
            <li class="left-align light" style="padding-left:0.5em">
                If you are interested, you can see the schedule available on the Trip Book, fill in the number of travelers, then click "BOOK NOW" for more.
            </li>
          </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="page-footer red lighten-2">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col l6 s12">
          <h5 class="white-text">By Local, From Local</h5>
          <p class="grey-text text-lighten-4"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-copyright">
      <div class="container">
      Made by PARADiSE Team using 
      <a class="brown-text text-lighten-3" href="http://materializecss.com" target="blank">Materialize</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>


  <!--  Scripts-->
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>

  </body>
</html>